---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | Mayan K Wellness" headerTheme="light">

    <!-- MAIN LAYOUT -->
    <main style="width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 160px 24px 100px 24px; box-sizing: border-box;">
        
        <!-- Terms Content Container -->
        <div style="background-color: #f4ebd9; border-radius: 16px; padding: 72px 80px; width: 100%; max-width: 820px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            
            <h1 style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 48px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
                Terms of Service
            </h1>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Agreement</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                    By accessing this website or purchasing coaching services from [Your Name], (acting as [Your Business Name]), you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use this website or purchase services.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Coaching services</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
                    The coaching services offered through this website are for educational and personal development purposes. I am a certified wellness coach, not a licensed therapist, psychologist, or medical professional.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                    Coaching is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. If you are experiencing a medical or mental health emergency, please contact your local emergency services or a healthcare provider.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Booking and payment</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Discovery calls are free of charge and can be booked through the scheduling tool on this website.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Paid sessions and programmes are billed as described on the Services page. Payment is due at the time of booking unless otherwise agreed.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">All prices are listed in [currency] and are inclusive of applicable taxes unless otherwise stated.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Cancelation and rescheduling</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">I ask for at least 24 hours notice if you need to cancel or reschedule a session. Cancellations made with less than 24 hours notice may be charged in full.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">If I need to cancel or reschedule a session, I will give you as much notice as possible and offer an alternative time.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Refunds</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;"><strong>Self-paced programmes:</strong> Due to the digital nature of these products, refunds are not available once access has been granted.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;"><strong>Group programmes:</strong> A full refund is available if you withdraw within 7 days of purchase, provided the programme has not yet started. Once the programme has started, refunds are not available.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"><strong>1:1 coaching packages:</strong> A pro-rated refund may be available for unused sessions if you wish to discontinue coaching. This is assessed on a case-by-case basis.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Confidentiality</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">Everything discussed during coaching sessions is confidential. I will not share your personal information or session content with anyone without your explicit consent, except where I am legally required to do so (for example, if there is a risk of harm to yourself or others).</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Intellectual property</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">All content on this website, including text, images, graphics, and design, is owned by [Your Name] and is protected by copyright law. You may not reproduce, distribute, or use any content from this website without written permission.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">Materials provided as part of coaching programmes (worksheets, guides, resources) are for your personal use only and may not be shared or redistributed.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Limitation of liability</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Coaching is a collaborative process and results vary depending on individual circumstances and effort. I do not guarantee specific outcomes from coaching services.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">To the fullest extent permitted by law, I am not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of this website or coaching services.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Governing law</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">These terms are governed by the laws of [your jurisdiction]. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of [your jurisdiction].</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Changes to these terms</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">I may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of this website or services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c3338; margin-bottom: 12px;">Contact</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 300; color: #55524d; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">If you have any questions about these terms, contact me at [your@email.com].</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

</BaseLayout>
